1a:["$","section","Standard Deduction 与 1040X 的关系-7",{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"Standard Deduction 与 1040X 的关系"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"很多留学生误把 Standard Deduction 当成“必然能用”的减税项，但在非居民路径中通常不可用。若因为误用 Standard Deduction 导致报税错误，后续可能需要 1040X 修正表来调整。先判定身份再选扣除项，可以显著降低修正成本。"}]]}]]}]
