1c:["$","section","免责声明（必须先看清楚）-9",{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"免责声明（必须先看清楚）"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/75","children":[["$","p","0",{"children":"本文为判断指导与经验整理，非 CPA/EA 或税务执业建议。F1 / OPT 报税身份判定涉及个人停留记录与材料情况，若不确定，请先使用工具做判断或寻求专业帮助。"}]]}]]}]
1d:["$","section",null,{"className":"mt-12","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold","children":"FAQ"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 grid gap-3","children":[["$","details","SPT 测试一定会让我变成 Resident 吗？",{"className":"rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/90 p-4 text-sm text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-brand-ink","children":"SPT 测试一定会让我变成 Resident 吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"不一定。F1 的前五个日历年通常属于 exempt 年限，但仍需结合当年停留记录判断。"}]]}],["$","details","我只拿 W-2，也需要考虑 1040-NR 吗？",{"className":"rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/90 p-4 text-sm text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-brand-ink","children":"我只拿 W-2，也需要考虑 1040-NR 吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"需要。表格路径取决于身份，而不是收入类型。"}]]}],["$","details","TurboTax 可以处理 1040-NR 吗？",{"className":"rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/90 p-4 text-sm text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-brand-ink","children":"TurboTax 可以处理 1040-NR 吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"TurboTax 更面向居民路径，非居民路径通常需要 Sprintax 或其他方式。"}]]}],["$","details","如果我判断错了，会有什么后果？",{"className":"rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/90 p-4 text-sm text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-brand-ink","children":"如果我判断错了，会有什么后果？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"可能需要修正申报、补材料或重新填写，增加时间成本。"}]]}],["$","details","我已经是第 6 个日历年就一定是 Resident 吗？",{"className":"rounded-[20px] border border-brand-pink/30 bg-white/90 p-4 text-sm text-brand-ink/70","children":[["$","summary",null,{"className":"cursor-pointer font-semibold text-brand-ink","children":"我已经是第 6 个日历年就一定是 Resident 吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-3","children":"不一定，还需要结合 SPT 测试与当年停留天数综合判断。"}]]}]]}]]}]
